'''2019年亚洲公路自行车锦标赛'''是第39届[[亚洲自行车锦标赛|亚洲公路自行车锦标赛]]，于2019年4月23日至28日在乌兹别克斯坦塔什干进行<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://accasia.org/content/2019-asian-road-cycling-championships|title=2019 Asian Road Cycling Championships|work=Asian Cycling Confederation|access-date=2019-04-08|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191030221106/http://accasia.org/content/2019-asian-road-cycling-championships|archivedate=2019-10-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>，比赛精英组共设六个小项<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://2019accroadchamp.uz/files/arc19_programme_day.pdf|title=2019 Asian Road Cycling Championships Tashkent – Programme|website=2019accroadchamp.uz|access-date=2019-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190426103344/http://2019accroadchamp.uz/files/arc19_programme_day.pdf|archive-date=2019-04-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。这是乌兹别克斯坦首次主办亚洲自行车锦标赛<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tashkenttimes.uz/sports/2967-uzbekistan-to-host-asian-cycling-championships-2019|title=Uzbekistan to host Asian Cycling Championships 2019|publisher=The Tashkent Times|date=2018-10-02|accessdate=2020-09-30|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190905142936/http://tashkenttimes.uz/sports/2967-uzbekistan-to-host-asian-cycling-championships-2019|archivedate=2019-09-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

